<lb n="2"/>śrī<surplus><g type="danda"/></surplus>-mahendrapāladeva-rājye 
<lb n="3"/>bhi<choice><sic><unclear>ch</unclear></sic><corr>kṣ</corr></choice>u-sujayagarbheṇa vuddha<lb 
n="4" break="no"/>-bhaṭṭārakāya pradatta<supplied reason="omitted">ḥ</supplied> sta<lb 
n="5" break="no"/>mbho 'yaṁ satvārthahetoḥ

 <g type="danda"/></p>
