         <div type="translation">
<p n="1">During the reign of  Śrī Mahendrapāladeva, year 5, on the seventh day of <supplied reason="explanation">the month of</supplied> Śrāvaṇa, the monk <supplied reason="explanation">named</supplied> Sujayagarbha offered this pillar to the Lord Buddha for the welfare of <supplied reason="subaudible">all</supplied> beings.</p>
          </div>
